Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:51.48,White,,0,0,0,,que disparar per defensar-se.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:53.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Podria ser...\Nque aquest home fos..."
